      public void SetUniversity(University newUniversity)

    • SetProfessor

      public void SetProfessor(Professor newProfessor)
      Set a new professor to the course. The course can only have one professor, their university must be the same. If we set a professor to a course which it already has one, the old professor will be removed.
      Parameters:
      newProfessor - course's new professor
